# Bauhaus theme

When editing **`components/themes/bauhaus/**`** or implementing **Bauhaus / constructivist** UI:

1. Read **`.cursor/agents/skills/bauhaus-theme.md`** (tokens, motion, layout, checklist).
2. Use **semantic + `--rv-*`** tokens from `bauhaus-light` / `bauhaus-dark` in `app/globals.css`.
3. **frontend-developer**; handoff should include `bauhaus-theme.md` for full-page or component work in this style.

For theme plumbing (new preset, `data-theme`), use **`theme-instructions.md`**.
